sequenceDiagram
    participant EB as EventBridge<br/>(1min rule)
    participant HC as Health Check Lambda
    participant CW as CloudWatch
    participant SFN as Step Functions
    participant FL as Failover Lambda
    participant AURORA_P as Aurora Primary
    participant AURORA_DR as Aurora DR
    participant R53 as Route 53
    participant SNS as SNS Alert

    EB->>HC: Trigger health check
    HC->>AURORA_P: DescribeDBClusters
    HC->>CW: Put health metric
    
    alt Primary Healthy
        HC-->>CW: HealthStatus = 1
    else Primary Unhealthy
        HC-->>CW: HealthStatus = 0
        CW->>SFN: Alarm → StartExecution
        SFN->>FL: PromoteReadReplica
        FL->>AURORA_DR: PromoteReadReplicaDBCluster
        AURORA_DR-->>FL: Cluster promoted to Writer
        FL->>R53: ChangeResourceRecordSets (flip DR)
        FL->>AURORA_P: ModifyDBCluster (demote)
        FL->>SNS: Publish failover notification
        SNS-->>Ops: PagerDuty / Email alert
    end